  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK987">
<l>iṉṉācey tārkku miṉiyavē ceyyākkā</l>
<l>leṉṉa payattatō cālpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of what avail is perfect goodness if it cannot do pleasing things even to those who have pained (it) ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
